title: The Westside Boogie Interview: Becoming Super Blood, Writing on Kendrick's Album & More
description:
WS Boogie stopped by before the release of his new album, to chat with Adam on his growth, going to therapy, fatherhood, Eminem stories, working process, going back to the hood, flirting with our very own Gina, and more! https://www.instagram.com/westsideboo...

-----
00:00 Intro
1:20 Boogie says he likes Gina
1:45 Boogie salutes Adam for having all these personalities on the platform
3:15 Gina joins the interview, they go at each other and talk about their relationship 
6:59 Boogie is appreciative that people still care about him dropping new music
8:30 Adam wants to know who reached out to whom first, Boogie acted like he wanted to work
12:15 Boogie says KB Devaughn has a whole verse dropping about Gina
14:30 Which song made Eminem sign Boogie?
15:35 Boogie tells an exclusive story about Eminem going back to his hood on a bicycle
19:50 Boogie thought it was smart to hide everything from his kids until he realized he was already kinda accustomed to it 
26:40 Going to therapy made him aware of certain things so he doesn't rap everything in an ignorant way the way he used to. Seeing results from therapy after going for a year
28:29 Julie Greenwald from Atlantic wanted to sign Boogie just because he told her he got shot
36:00 Boogie was at Teanna Trump's birthday party w/ Adam
37:27 Boogie simply searches for "big black ass" on p___ sites
39:18 Boogie reviews Kendrick's album + Writing for Summer Walker for Kendrick's album
43:33 Vlad blocked Boogie on socials after he told him it was insensitive to post a Mac Miller comparison after he passed 
46:31 Boogie breaks down the vision for his album, being the best, but also inspiring to heal the community and support the trauma, show the light and show different sides of who he is
49:13 Boogie says he's the king of LA right now
52:34 Gina was hoping Boogie would propose to her on this podcast
53:51 Boogie clearly tells Gina he likes her, then she turns into shy mode
59:00 Boogie hooked up with Celina Powell, despite fans and his DJ telling him not to, and she thought he was A Boogie
1:01:52 Boogie didn't learn his lesson and had sex with Celina Powell a year later
